<TEXT>
<P>
LUANDA, April 15 (Xinhua) -- A senior OAU official Wednesday
calls on both the Angolan government and the opposition National
Union for the Total Independence of Angola (UNITA) to make
continued efforts to achieve final peace in the country.
</P>
