important progress with China on this," she told a gathering at
the Institute for International Economics Conference. But she did
not elaborate. It was reported earlier that Barshefsky would go to
Beijing probably by the end of this month to continue the tough
negotiations with China. (US-China-WTO)
</P>
<P>
