with Mahathir centered on the financial problems as well as the
haze facing ASEAN at present.
</P>
<P>
He said that Mahathir stressed the need for ASEAN to stand
united in facing the currency crisis.
</P>
<P>
"He (Mahathir) was particularly concerned with efforts in
dealing with the changing financial structure of the international
system," the ASEAN secretary-general said.
</P>
<P>
Severino said Mahathir also stressed the necessity for ASEAN to
work together to overcome the haze problem as it affects everyone
in the region.
</P>
<P>
Mahathir also stressed the need to mobilize international
assistance," Severino said.
</P>
