Treaty Organization (NATO), said Portuguese President Jorge
Sampaio here Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Sampaio, who is on his first state visit to Ukraine, made this
point at a joint news conference with his Ukrainian counterpart
Leonid Kuchma. His visit is from April 13 to 16.
</P>
<P>
Sampaio will back Ukraine's bid to consolidate its democracy
and independence. He vowed to make special efforts to draw Ukraine
close to the Western European Union.
</P>
