cooperation with European institutions and complete its
cooperation projects.
</P>
<P>
Sampaio visited the Chornobyl nuclear power station early
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
In a summit on Tuesday, Sampaio said he supported Ukraine's bid
to become an associate member of the EU in the near future.
</P>
<P>
Sampaio also had separate talks on Tuesday with Ukrainian Prime
Minister Valery Pustovoitenko, chairman of the Supreme Soviet
(Parliament) Alexander Moroz and Foreign Minister Gennady Udovenko.
</P>
<P>
