<HEADLINE> Real Madrid And Juventus Meet in Cup Final </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, April 15 (Xinhua) -- Real Madrid will meet Juventus in
this year's European Cup Final at the Amsterdam Arena on May 20.
</P>
<P>
The two clubs have met 24 times in all three club competitions,
but never in a final.
</P>
<P>
Real, who have won the European Cup a record six times, knocked
out reigning champions Borussia Dortmund 2-0 on aggregate after
the second leg of their semifinal ended in a 0-0 draw in Dortmund
on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Juventus, European champions in 1996 and runners-up to Dortmund
last year, lost the second leg of their semifinal 3-2 to Monaco
but came through 6-4 on aggregate to reach the European Cup final
for the third successive season. 
</P>
